{
  "texts": [
    "The protocol was not amended or changed.",
    "Further information on research design is available in the Nature Portfolio Reporting Summary linked to this article.",
    "The PubMed database search yielded 622 unique publications; another 18 guidelines were identified through other sources: 8 guidelines were identified through a search of the EQUATOR Network's library of reporting guidelines, two guidelines were identified through review of recommendations of federal agencies; one additional guideline was included based on review of journal recommendations.",
    "Another seven additional guidelines were added as incidental findings.",
    "After removal of duplicates, 630 publications were subjected to the screening process."
  ]
}